text:
Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2017 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2017 has been repealed by section 31 of the Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2017
